name: CSIndexError.Code
desc: Error codes that describe indexing-specific errors.

items.name: case indexingUnsupported
items.desc: Indexing isn't supported on the device.

items.name: case invalidClientStateError
items.desc: The provided client state data is invalid.

items.name: case quotaExceeded
items.desc: The quota for the bundle has been exceeded.

items.name: case remoteConnectionError
items.desc: An error occurred while communicating with the remote process.
